      <title>kubernetes glusterfs 연동</title>
      <link>https://kimpaper.github.io/posts/kube/2020-05-13-kubernetes-glusterfs/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2020 11:18:00 +0000</pubDate>
